node.title: Serious crash shuts part of SH16 northbound lanes
node.description: A serious crash has shut a section of State Highway 16 near the Auckland suburb of Rosebank this afternoon.
node.content:
["A serious crash has shut a section of State Highway 16 near the Auckland suburb of Rosebank this afternoon.", "", "
A serious crash on SH16 on 23 February has shut a section of the northbound lanes on the highway. Photo: NZTA
", "The northbound lane on SH16 has been closed between Rosebank Road and Patiki Road since about 4pm.", "Waka Kotahi Follow the short detour and expect long delays.", "In an update just after 5.15pm, the transport agency said police were on-site with a serious crash investigation underway, which was expected to take a few hours."]
